<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM1.3">
<l>pirāṉeṉṟu taṉṉaippaṉ ṉāḷpara vittoḻu vāriṭarkaṇ</l>
<l>ṭirāṉeṉṉa niṟkiṉṟa vīcaṉkaṇ ṭīriṉa vaṇṭukiṇṭip</l>
<l>porāniṉṟa koṉṟaip potumpark kiṭantupom meṉṟuṟaivā</l>
<l>yarāniṉ ṟiraikkuñ caṭaiccempoṉ nīṇmuṭi yantaṇaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord who stands there, look, of whom they think “he is not seeing the affliction</l>
<l>of those who rever and worship him as master”, is the brahmin with a red-golden long crown</l>
<l>of matted hair where snakes with poison-bag mouths stay [and] hiss suddenly,</l>
<l>lying in groves of Laburnum where bees in swarms keep probing [and] fighting.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
